{"id":918,"parent_id":909,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":918,"title":"Amos 9","subtitle":"","short_title":"Amos","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 9"],[".studySummary",["i","Israel will be sifted among all nations—In the last days, the people of Israel will be gathered again into their own land, and it will become productive."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.1","order":"02.31.009.61520"},["b","1"],"I saw the Lord standing upon the altar: and he said, Smite the lintel of the door, that the posts may shake: and cut them in the head, all of them; and I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"slay"],"the last of them with the sword: he that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"fleeth"],"of them shall not flee away, and he that escapeth of them shall not be delivered."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.2","order":"02.31.009.61521"},["b","2"],"Though they dig into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"hell"],", thence shall mine hand take them; though they climb up to heaven, thence will I bring them down:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.3","order":"02.31.009.61522"},["b","3"],"And though they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"hide"],"themselves in the top of Carmel, I will search and take them out thence; and though they be hid from my sight in the bottom of the sea, thence will I command the serpent, and he shall bite them:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.4","order":"02.31.009.61523"},["b","4"],"And though they go into captivity before their enemies, thence will I command the sword, and it shall slay them: and I will set mine eyes upon them for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"evil"],", and not for good."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.5","order":"02.31.009.61524"},["b","5"],"And the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"of hosts",["i","is"],"he that toucheth the land, and it shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"melt"],", and all that dwell therein shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"mourn"],": and it shall rise up wholly like a flood; and shall be drowned, as",["i","by"],"the flood of Egypt."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.6","order":"02.31.009.61525"},["b","6"],["i","It is"],"he that buildeth his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"stories"],"in the heaven, and hath founded his troop in the earth; he that calleth for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"waters"],"of the sea, and poureth them out upon the face of the earth: The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"his name."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.7","order":"02.31.009.61526"},["b","7"],["i","Are"],"ye not as children of the Ethiopians unto me, O children of Israel? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],". Have not I brought up Israel out of the land of Egypt? and the Philistines from Caphtor, and the Syrians from Kir?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.8","order":"02.31.009.61527"},["b","8"],"Behold, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"eyes"],"of the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],["i","are"],"upon the sinful kingdom, and I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"destroy"],"it from off the face of the earth; saving that I will not utterly",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"destroy"],"the house of Jacob, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.9","order":"02.31.009.61528"},["b","9"],"For, lo, I will command, and I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"sift"],"the house of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"Israel"],"among all nations, like as",["i","corn"],"is sifted in a sieve, yet shall not the least grain",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"fall"],"upon the earth."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.10","order":"02.31.009.61529"},["b","10"],"All the sinners of my people shall die by the sword, which say, The evil shall not overtake nor",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"prevent"],"us."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.11","order":"02.31.009.61530"},["b","11"],"¶In that day will I raise up the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"tabernacle"],"of David that is fallen, and close up the breaches thereof; and I will raise up his ruins, and I will build it as in the days of old:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.12","order":"02.31.009.61531"},["b","12"],"That they may",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"possess"],"the remnant of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"Edom"],", and of all the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"heathen"],", which are called by my name, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that doeth this."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.13","order":"02.31.009.61532"},["b","13"],"Behold, the days come, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that the plowman shall overtake the reaper, and the treader of grapes him that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"soweth"],"seed; and the mountains shall drop sweet wine, and all the hills shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"melt"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.14","order":"02.31.009.61533"},["b","14"],"And I will bring again the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"captivity"],"of my people of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Israel"],", and they shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"build"],"the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"waste"],"cities, and inhabit",["i","them;"],"and they shall plant vineyards, and drink the wine thereof; they shall also make gardens, and eat the fruit of them."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.15","order":"02.31.009.61534"},["b","15"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"plant"],"them upon their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"land"],", and they shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"no more"],"be pulled up out of their land which I have given them, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.1a","order":"02.31.009.61535"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.9"},"3 Ne. 16:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.1b","order":"02.31.009.61537"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/28.1"},"Prov. 28:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.14"},"Amos 2:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.2a","order":"02.31.009.61539"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/139.8.8-9"},"Ps. 139:8 (8–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.3a","order":"02.31.009.61541"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/12.10"},"2 Ne. 12:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.14"},"Alma 12:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.4a","order":"02.31.009.61543"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/21.10"},"Jer. 21:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.5a","order":"02.31.009.61545"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.25.23-25"},"D&C 101:25 (23–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.5b","order":"02.31.009.61547"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.8"},"Amos 8:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.6a","order":"02.31.009.61549"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.33"},"Moses 1:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.6b","order":"02.31.009.61551"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.8"},"Amos 5:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.7.6-7"},"Moses 2:7 (6–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.9.9-10"},"Abr. 4:9 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.8a","order":"02.31.009.61553"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/34.15"},"Ps. 34:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.1"},"D&C 1:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.7"},"38:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/67.2"},"67:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.8b","order":"02.31.009.61555"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.33"},"D&C 5:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.8c","order":"02.31.009.61557"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.11"},"Jer. 30:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.3.2-4"},"2 Ne. 3:3 (2–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/6.11.10-11"},"6:11 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/20.20.20-21"},"20:20 (20–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.9a","order":"02.31.009.61559"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.9b","order":"02.31.009.61561"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-ten-lost-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Ten Lost Tribes of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.9c","order":"02.31.009.61563"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.6"},"Mal. 3:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.10a","order":"02.31.009.61565"},["b","10a"],["span.small","HEB"],"confront."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.11a","order":"02.31.009.61567"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.16.15-17"},"Acts 15:16 (15–17)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temple"},"TG Temple"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.12a","order":"02.31.009.61569"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/obad/1.17"},"Obad. 1:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.2.1-2"},"2 Ne. 24:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.12b","order":"02.31.009.61571"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",